text: Dmitri Aleksandrovich Starodub (; born 19 May 1995) is a Russian football player. He plays for FC Tver. ==Club career== He made his Russian Premier League debut on 21 March 2015 for FC Arsenal Tula in a game against PFC CSKA Moscow. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Sportspeople from Vladivostok Category:Living people Category:Russian footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:FC Dynamo Moscow reserves players Category:Russian Premier League players Category:FC Arsenal Tula players
